text=! Ubuntu Linux ²[[http://www.ubuntulinux.org | Ubuntu]] is a Linux supported by Mark Shuttleworth, based on the Debian Packaging.²²* Great usability, nice grafical features, still some problems with my custom kernel on my Tibook G4.²* If you install from CD be sure to set "Autoneg on" with the ethtool otherwise your Sungem card will not be funking.²* Kernel Config for PPC Tibook G4, Attach:config-2.6.12.2.txt - The Ubuntu default 5.0.4 Kernel config is to loaded for my taste.²* [[http://www-128.ibm.com/developerworks/linux/library/l-tip-prompt/index.html | Prompt Magic]] by Daniel Robbins. The final prompt for me: [= export PS1="\[\e[32;1m\]\w> \[\e[0m\]" =]²* Attach:xorg-conf.txt
targets=
